90515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001727_869881301223848_4956483551034422676_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=c_P9j6AYrbIQ7kNvgHJyGR4&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AFGoX53yfqA-x4U8JqvbrId&oh=00_AYCFVPkPOXhAi_tLaXXd3cEE1rcFbVsPnsdzNKnMHNaLGQ&oe=66E6C85D"}, {"file_name": "5.png", "id": "1029913311618453", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75280177_1029913314951786_1716028478303834469_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=C2JOgLrbKEcQ7kNvgHsMGhI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AFGoX53yfqA-x4U8JqvbrId&oh=00_AYBePDDstX_CxPrNfcOBzLvRbRLN8EC5NcU_v5AvQiOf8A&oe=66E6CAA4"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Mini Games", "keywords": ["mini", "games", "puzzle", "casual", "table"], "long_description": "A collection of seated mini games including:\n\nRail Targets: Hit the targets, while riding in a rail carriage.\n\nPiece Puzzle: Connect the pieces of an object to complete the puzzle.\n\nUnblock The Road: Slide the blocks to connect the road.\n\nMinesweeper: Find all the mines and clear the grid.\n\nShell Game: Pick which cup the ball is in, after the cups have been moved around.\n\nKlondike Solitaire: The classic game of Klondike using playing cards.\n\nPyramid Solitaire: The classic card game where you have to find pairs that add up to 13.\n\nSpider Solitaire: A popular variation of solitaire with the option to play with either 1 suit or 2 suits, for increased difficulty.\n\nJigsaw Puzzle: Choose a picture and complete the puzzle.\n\nChess: The classic game of chess.\n\nCheckers: The classic game of checkers.\n\nWhack A Mole: Hit as many moles as you can, as fast as you can.\n\nWire Loop Game: Move the hoop along the wire, within the time limit.\n\nShooting Gallery: Get as many points as you can, by shooting the objects.\n\nMarble Solitaire: Complete the game by removing all the balls, but one, from the board.\n\nCarnival Rail: Throw baseballs and hoops at the carnival style targets, while riding in a rail carriage.", "short_description": "A collection of seated mini games:\n\nRail Targets: Hit the targets riding a carriage.\nPiece Puzzle: Connect the pieces.\nUnblock The Road: Slide the blocks.\nMinesweeper\nShell Game: Which cup is the ball in?\nKlondike Solitaire\nPyramid Solitaire\nSpider Solitaire\nJigsaw Puzzle: Complete the puzzle.\nChess\nCheckers\nWhack A Mole\nWire Loop Game: Move the hoop along the wire.\nShooting Gallery: Get as many points as you can.\nMarble Solitaire\nCarnival Rail: Throw baseballs and hoops, riding in a carriage."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://mobilefusionapps.com/privacypolicyvr.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MobileFusion Apps LTD", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://mobilefusionapps.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8077642515685081"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75367591_935546914479423_293927678659637453_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=h0N8a_Xhpa4Q7kNvgFD3q0z&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AFGoX53yfqA-x4U8JqvbrId&oh=00_AYB7iiTLrgQ64YHfxUWSqHo0Tq6LG3nLBUNNRWRfpmE8cQ&oe=66E6B84E"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": 